      "DialogueText_10_10D44AC44144EC85326507BD9E2D1C2A": "NSLOCTEXT(\"\", \"34746B3D407D7B54BB4B7BA6B80AF383\", \"Hello, you two. If you\\'re hearing this, then you\\'ve chosen to place your trust in me. Thank you.\")",
